    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Speak with Animals</strong> (Level 1 Divination)</p><p>You gain the ability to comprehend and verbally communicate with beasts for the duration. The knowledge and awareness of many beasts is limited by their intelligence, but at a minimum, beasts can give you information about nearby locations and monsters, including whatever they can perceive or have perceived within the past day. You might be able to persuade a beast to perform a small favor for you, at the GM's discretion.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Self | <strong>Duration:</strong> 10 minutes (Ritual)</p><p><em>Classes: Bard, Druid, Ranger</em></p>",
